            <title>[CASSANDRA-10012] Deadlock when session streaming is retried after exception</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-10012</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This patch ensures that the CompressedInputStream thread is cleaned up properly (for example, if an Exception occurs and a session stream is retried).&lt;/p&gt;</description>
